title: BrainUp
details: BrainUp is a quiz website where users can participate in quizzes on different topics listed on the website.

title: Vivid Learning
details: Vivid Learning is a learning platform website.In this website users can register and login, can view courses and can download pdf of any course they like.

title: The Fitness Factory
details: It is a fitness activity website completed with ReactJS and used Local Storage to save users input of activity which they chooses.

title: Super 5
details: Super 5 is fantasy football player selection website.Users can select five footballer of their chosen and make a team by spending budget for players,coach,manager and they see the total budget they have spent.
